### simpleDB HTTP SQL Demo (.rest)


### 适用于 VS Code REST Client 扩展


### 执行顺序：从上到下逐条 Send Request
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:18080
@loginPath = /auth/login
@registerPath = /auth/register
@activatePath = /auth/activate
@sqlPath = /sql/execute
@grantPath = /sql/grant
@table = demo_users
@grantUser = demo_user_1
@grantUserPassword = 123456


### 1) 登录（默认管理员）
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}{{loginPath}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "sdb",
  "password": "simpleDB"
}


### 从登录响应提取 token
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.token.accessToken}}


### 1.1) 注册普通用户
# @name registerUser
POST {{baseUrl}}{{registerPath}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{grantUser}}",
  "password": "{{grantUserPassword}}",
  "displayName": "Demo User"
}


### 1.2) 激活普通用户（需要 super_admin）
# @name activateUser
POST {{baseUrl}}{{activatePath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{grantUser}}"
}


### 1.3) 给普通用户授权当前库（库级绑定）
# @name grantUserDatabase
POST {{baseUrl}}{{grantPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "database": "demo_transport",
  "username": "{{grantUser}}"
}


### 2) 建表
# @name createTable
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "CREATE TABLE {{table}} (id int PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT, username string UNIQUE REQUIRED, age int DEFAULT 0)"
}


### 3) 单条插入（参数化）
# @name insertOne
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "INSERT INTO {{table}} (username, age) VALUES (:username, :age)",
  "paramMap": {
    "username": "alice",
    "age": 20
  }
}


### 4) 批量插入
# @name insertBatch
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "INSERT INTO {{table}} (username, age) VALUES (?, ?), (?, ?)",
  "paramList": ["bob", 21, "carol", 22]
}


### 5) 批量更新（参数化 IN）
# @name updateBatch
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "UPDATE {{table}} SET age=:age WHERE id IN :ids",
  "paramMap": {
    "age": 30,
    "ids": [
      1,
      2,
      3
    ]
  }
}


### 6) 字段投影查询（只返回 id 和 username）
# @name selectProjection
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT id, username FROM {{table}} WHERE username = ?",
  "paramList": ["alice"]
}


### 7) 混合参数查询（paramMap + paramList + 分页）
# @name selectMixedPage
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM {{table}} WHERE age >= :minAge AND username != ? ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT ? OFFSET ?",
  "paramMap": {
    "minAge": 20
  },
  "paramList": ["alice", 2, 1]
}


### 7.1) LIKE 模糊查询（查找用户名以 'a' 开头的用户）
# @name selectLike
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM {{table}} WHERE username LIKE ?",
  "paramList": ["a%"]
}


### 7.2) 内置分页查询（PAGE/SIZE 语法）
# @name selectPageSize
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM {{table}} PAGE ? SIZE ?",
  "paramList": [1, 2]
}


### 8) 全表聚合（COUNT / AVG / MAX / MIN）
# @name selectAgg
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT COUNT(*) AS total, AVG(age) AS avg_age, MAX(age) AS max_age, MIN(age) AS min_age FROM {{table}}"
}


### 9) GROUP BY 分组统计
# @name selectGroupBy
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT age, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM {{table}} GROUP BY age ORDER BY cnt DESC"
}


### 10) 验证：无条件删除会被拒绝（应返回 400）
# @name deleteWithoutWhere
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "DELETE FROM {{table}}"
}

### ── JOIN 链表查询演示 ──────────────────────────────────────────


### 13) 建从表 demo_orders
# @name createOrders
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "CREATE TABLE demo_orders (id int PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT, user_id int REQUIRED, amount int DEFAULT 0)"
}


### 14) 向 demo_orders 插入数据（user_id=3 关联 carol，user_id=99 不存在用于 LEFT JOIN 测试）
# @name insertOrders
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "INSERT INTO demo_orders (user_id, amount) VALUES (?, ?), (?, ?), (?, ?)",
  "paramList": [3, 100, 3, 200, 99, 50]
}


### 15) INNER JOIN：只返回两表都匹配的行
# @name innerJoin
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM demo_orders INNER JOIN demo_users ON demo_orders.user_id = demo_users.id"
}


### 16) LEFT JOIN：demo_orders 全部保留，user_id=99 对应 demo_users 字段为 null
# @name leftJoin
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM demo_orders LEFT JOIN demo_users ON demo_orders.user_id = demo_users.id"
}


### 17) JOIN + 字段投影 + WHERE + ORDER BY
# @name joinWithFilter
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT demo_orders.id, demo_users.username, demo_orders.amount FROM demo_orders INNER JOIN demo_users ON demo_orders.user_id = demo_users.id WHERE demo_orders.amount >= 100 ORDER BY demo_orders.amount DESC"
}


### ── IN / NOT IN 子查询演示 ──────────────────────────────────────


### 18) NOT IN 字面量：排除指定 id
# @name notInLiteral
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM {{table}} WHERE id NOT IN (?, ?)",
  "paramList": [1, 2]
}


### 19) IN 子查询：查询有订单的用户（user_id 在 demo_orders 中存在）
# @name inSubquery
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM demo_users WHERE id IN (SELECT user_id FROM demo_orders)"
}


### 20) NOT IN 子查询：查询没有订单的用户
# @name notInSubquery
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM demo_users WHERE id NOT IN (SELECT user_id FROM demo_orders)"
}


### 21) IN 子查询 + 子查询带 WHERE：只查高金额订单关联的用户
# @name inSubqueryWithFilter
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM demo_users WHERE id IN (SELECT user_id FROM demo_orders WHERE amount >= ?)",
  "paramList": [200]
}


### 11) 条件删除（允许）
# @name deleteWithWhere
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "DELETE FROM {{table}} WHERE id IN (?, ?)",
  "paramList": [1, 2]
}


### 12) 删除后再查一次（验证结果）
# @name selectAfterDelete
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sqlPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM {{table}}"
}